HEADWORD: Piscary
<hw>Pis"ca*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>piscarius</ets> relating to fishes or to fishing, fr.
<ets>piscis</ets> a fish.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The right or
privilege of fishing in another man's waters.</def>
